data.title: I enjoy coming here everytime I go.
data.text: This is a hidden gem in Kenner Louisiana. It's a great bar to go to and they have a great food menu.  I can get the best of both worlds. The bar-tenders are very nice. The owner is usually on site to greet the patrons. There open for lunch and dinner. The beers that I drink are always ice cold. They have daily food specials and I have never had a bad meal there. It's a must go if you are in Kenner Louisiana.
